# Plan 12: Gallery with Lightbox

## Goal
Implement a photo/video gallery with a masonry layout and lightbox modal.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create `app/gallery/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Install a lightbox library (e.g., `yet-another-react-lightbox` or custom).
- [ ] Implement a masonry grid layout for images.
- [ ] Fetch gallery images from the database.
- [ ] Add category filtering (Live, Studio, Press).
- [ ] Enable clicking an image to open it in the lightbox.
